		"Id": "mechdef_wraith_TRNW",
		"Name": "Wraith",
		"Details": "Originally created by an eccentric mercenary operating within the Lyran half of the Federated Commonwealth, the TRNW made the rather bold choice to do away with its traditional energy weapons loadout for a missile payload. Supposedly presented to Curtiss Militech as the next step in the Wraith’s evolution, the inability to reliably source the extreme amounts of Clan tech used within the original design limited possible wide-scale production. Some rumors say the design was considered for Operation BULLDOG, though such claims have been largely disproven. Nevertheless, a number of TRNW chassis have been seen in both mercenary companies and House armies, though in limited numbers.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>COMMUNITY CONTENT</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_wraith"
	},
